      <title>eZOracle 2.1.0 and 2.0.4 released</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ezoracle/news/ezoracle_2_1_0_and_2_0_4_released</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;2.1.0 is the same version that you'll find bundled with eZ Publish 4.4.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2.0.4 is the bugfix release for eZ Publish versions 4.1 to 4.3.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Besides bugfixes, the main new thing is support for the eZDFS cluster mode.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
