      <title>eZ Oracle 2.0.2 released</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ezoracle/news/ez_oracle_2_0_2_released</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; The latest version of the "eZ Publish database extension for Oracle", also known as eZ Oracle, &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;

&lt;li&gt;adds full compatibility for eZ Publish up to 4.2.0&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;adds full compatibility for php 5.3&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;fixes two bugs related to update/install scripts&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
