      <title>eZ Oracle 1.8.2 released</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ezoracle/news/ez_oracle_1_8_2_released</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hot on the heels of the eZ Publish 4.0.4 release, this new version of the "eZ Publish database adapter for oracle" brings:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;

&lt;li&gt;a bugfix for transactions that would be committed halfway in some particular cases&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;database update scripts to update your eZ Publish installation to 4.0.4&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; It can be downloaded here: &lt;a href="/ezoracle/downloads/ez_oracle_1_8/ezoracle_1_8_2_zip" target="_self"&gt;ezoracle-1.8.2.zip&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Enjoy! &lt;/p&gt;</description>
