      <title>eZ Oracle 1.8.1 released</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ezoracle/news/ez_oracle_1_8_1_released</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am happy to announce the eZ Oracle 1.8.1 release! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;5 bugs have been fixed, and compatibility with eZ Publish 4.0.2 and 4.0.3 restored.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please make sure to read with care the release notes and install/upgrade instructions. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In particular, when running upgrade scripts, use the initurlaliasmlid.php script that comes in the "patches" directory of the extension instead of the one that is part of the standard 4.0.2/4.0.3 installation&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Gaetano Giunta)</author>
